	<h1 class="title">XP 之后，Windows 7 成了微软的另一个阻碍</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/113378/small/113378.jpg?1435590009" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">周韶宏 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-03 08:49:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11586/medium/11586.jpg?1436638337" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


